TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {1599=The final show of July...and what an ending to our annual "space month".  New music from Chicago Afrobeat Project (who were just in town with special guest Tony Allen), Talisman, earlyW~Rm, Dubology, The Cat Empire (also in town recently), Ramon Judah & Conscious Sound, Dub Club (ft. Natty King & King Stitt), Righteous Dub (dubbing GPGDS), Greg Dubamix, Taj Weekes & Adowa (live), Zion Dirty Sound, Dub Conscious, Piper St. Sound, International Observer, and Doctah X. On top of this we aired Dr. StrangeDub's interview of the incredible Brazilian guitarist/singer/songwriter Badi Assad, plus several of her songs. Rounding out the show with one more space-oriented set, plus a few other things from the likes of: Ital Roots Players, Radiola Dub Sound System, Tipsy, The Clash, The Dropsteppers, Little Tempo, Easy Star All Stars, Owen Gray, Scientist, Ramsey Lewis (& Earth Wind & Fire), Derrick Morgan, and more.}
